# Build outputs
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Visual Studio / MSBuild
.vs/
*.user
*.userosscache
*.suo
*.cache
*.FileListAbsolute.txt
*.rsuser
project.lock.json
artifacts/

# Rider / VS Code (optional local tooling)
.idea/
.vscode/
